{"tid":474823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個條友唔識又要扮識既例子","createTime":"2017-11-20T13:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T12:52:21.000Z","uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ed090806390507ee199983a89d89ea42b09d9aaf","tid":474823,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"話說有日成班朋友傾計去過邊到旅行<br />\n有條友鳩吹自己去過美國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話用一個禮拜遊撚哂成個美國<br />\n一聽就知佢9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =me<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =傻鳩<br />\n<br />\nMe: 你去左美國邊到玩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傻鳩: 我去完三藩市再去加州呀仲有去 blah blah blah<br />\nMe: (乜撚野呀 三藩市係加州既城市喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 哦係咩！仲有去邊呀？<br />\n傻鳩: 同埋有搭個d巴士由加州個邊去芝加哥，坐撚死人呀！<br />\nMe: (再吹大d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 搭左幾耐？<br />\n傻鳩: 坐左十鳩幾粒鐘！坐撚到屎忽爛！<br />\n(有朋友已經忍唔撚住嘴角失守暗暗地恥笑)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到呢到，已經唔想再聽落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺撚明鳩up<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好可憐，未去過美國FF成咁，比佢吹到美帝仲細過台灣，希望佢有機會好好見識下個世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05248b12e095d2813ebf6cdd152df310eb9cefb1","tid":474823,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245aa864ccd8b7d29c32930ce1dcc2416e59c685","tid":474823,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" clas